---
/**
 * Appointment - formulário de agendamento
 */
---

<section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-gray-50">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-sky-900 mb-4 text-center">Agende uma consulta</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8 text-center">
        Entre em contato com nossa recepção para dúvidas gerais ou médicas. Nossos médicos atendem ou retornam chamadas urgentes.
      </p>
      <form class="space-y-4 p-8 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm">
        <div>
          <label for="clinic" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1">Escolha a clínica</label>
          <select id="clinic" name="clinic" class="w-full px-4 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-sky-500 focus:border-sky-500">
            <option>Clínica de Patologia</option>
            <option>Clínica de Neurologia</option>
            <option>Clínica de Cardiologia</option>
          </select>
        </div>
        <div>
          <label for="doctor" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1">Escolha o médico</label>
          <select id="doctor" name="doctor" class="w-full px-4 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-sky-500 focus:border-sky-500">
            <option>Ahmed Abdallah</option>
            <option>Mahmoud Begha</option>
          </select>
        </div>
        <button type="submit" class="w-full py-3 bg-sky-600 text-white font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-sky-700 transition-colors">
          Agendar consulta
        </button>
      </form>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
